{"tid":605554,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"幽遊白書中奇怪嘅一幕","createTime":"2018-03-25T18:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T06:49:23.000Z","uid":60436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5384772465ccf200c9949205481ca7483791cac8","tid":605554,"uid":60436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:30:33.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意睇幽遊白書，<br />\n但每次睇到呢幕都覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/021700_71b7e19fb975776a4d65338cc62a7c52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F021700_71b7e19fb975776a4d65338cc62a7c52.png&h=e7fcfe61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解幽助會主動叫雷禪食人肉呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知道幽助係戰鬥狂，鍾意打得盡興，<br />\n佢亦都唔會偏袒人類或者任何種族，<br />\n唔通佢打完仙水變成魔族連價值觀都變咗？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/022241_6aece097d81bb45f223e1a8042a42d16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F022241_6aece097d81bb45f223e1a8042a42d16.png&h=31094e48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/022245_131d867a9e64ebee655bc98b33853954.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F022245_131d867a9e64ebee655bc98b33853954.png&h=4c606885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明第三卷因為吸魂鬼食咗細路嘅靈魂而發嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/022249_df8783758c3fcc4c69d5abbe3efc29b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F022249_df8783758c3fcc4c69d5abbe3efc29b5.png&h=5e984327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第十四卷逼於無奈要殺醫師而苦惱（最後醫師無死到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"8bbdfb60ef319a89904f25fe67e18bab1e8bdbb1","tid":605554,"uid":151691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:33:20.000Z","msg":"試探姐我諗"},{"pid":"1fe3ee8a4b75ee42c3ce873a4a21ab3e82047744","tid":605554,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:33:39.000Z","msg":"魔族大隔世覺醒咗"},{"pid":"a452a46ba701690279c9c1b2717d708e15ce712a","tid":605554,"uid":22993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"動畫對白好似係話捉兩三個壞人比佢食"},{"pid":"cbd009d9de2ca39f06c658f055c443e3b18b3cdc","tid":605554,"uid":91982,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:39:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fe7512296f46cb1ef4214b6499e72164f22dc09","tid":605554,"uid":60436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a452a46ba701690279c9c1b2717d708e15ce712a","tid":605554,"uid":22993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"動畫對白好似係話捉兩三個壞人比佢食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T18:50:50.000Z","msg":"我都記得粵語版好似係咁講，<br />\n我每次睇到呢幕都諗係咪幽助經歷太多戰鬥，佢價值觀已經有好大嘅灰色地帶（雖然佢本身都已經係條hi hi仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），但都好難想像呢句說話會由佢親口講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82357dc9d42d43329fad281560f455e274001ea9","tid":605554,"uid":31384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:30:36.000Z","msg":"佢老豆一直好堅持唔食人<br />\n到佢虛弱到就死呢一刻都依然堅持住<br />\n幽助見到唔忍心"},{"pid":"67bf3e34f356a05244fe18ac2dc48a3a3cd62feb","tid":605554,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe7512296f46cb1ef4214b6499e72164f22dc09","tid":605554,"uid":60436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a452a46ba701690279c9c1b2717d708e15ce712a","tid":605554,"uid":22993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep